- OPPO: ColorOS 5.0 and later

- Meizu: Flyme

- Alibaba Cloud\\\\"s proprietary channel: Android SDK 3.6.0 and later

If this parameter is not provided in long text mode, the first non-empty value from Body or AndroidPopupBody is used.', example='示例长文本'),
      androidBigPictureUrl?: string(name='AndroidBigPictureUrl', description='The image URL in big picture mode. Currently supported on: Alibaba Cloud\\\\"s proprietary channel with Android SDK 3.6.0 or later.', example='https://imag.example.com/image.png'),
      androidBigTitle?: string(name='AndroidBigTitle', description='The title in long text mode. Length limit: 200 bytes (one Chinese character is counted as 3 bytes).

